{
  "id": "tapestry-delegation-routing-fallback-to-generic",
  "title": "Tapestry falls back to generic shuttle when no category patterns match",
  "description": "Checks that when a task's files don't match any category patterns and no explicit tag is set, Tapestry routes to the generic shuttle agent.",
  "phase": "experimental",
  "tags": ["experimental", "tapestry", "delegation-routing", "category"],
  "target": {
    "kind": "builtin-agent-prompt",
    "agent": "tapestry"
  },
  "executor": {
    "kind": "model-response",
    "provider": "openrouter",
    "model": "anthropic/claude-opus-4-20250514",
    "input": "You are executing /start-work. The following category agents are available:\n- shuttle-frontend: patterns [*.tsx, *.css]\n- shuttle-backend: patterns [*.go, src/api/**]\n- shuttle: fallback for unmatched tasks\n\nThe plan has one unchecked task:\n\n- [ ] Task 3/5: Update README documentation\n  **Files**: README.md, docs/setup.md\n  **What**: Update the README with new installation instructions and add a setup guide\n  **Acceptance**: README.md has updated installation section. docs/setup.md exists with step-by-step setup guide.\n\nWhich shuttle agent would you use to delegate this task?"
  },
  "evaluators": [
    {
      "kind": "llm-judge",
      "expectedAnyOf": ["generic shuttle", "plain shuttle", "fallback shuttle", "no category match", "does not match a category"],
      "forbiddenContains": ["shuttle-frontend", "shuttle-backend"]
    }
  ]
}
